</div></div></div><div class="col sqs-col-8 span-8"><div class="sqs-block html-block sqs-block-html" data-block-type="2" id="block-6291241f43efe0a8b312"><div class="sqs-block-content">

<div class="sqs-html-content">
  <h1 style="text-align:center;white-space:pre-wrap;">About Todd Pillion</h1><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;"><strong>Todd was elected to serve Virginia’s 40th Senatorial District on November 5, 2019.</strong> The 40th district includes Grayson, Lee, Scott, Washington, Smyth (part), Wise (part), Wythe (part), and the city of Bristol. Due to recent redistricting, Todd is the Republican incumbent in the newly created Senate District 6 which includes Buchanan, Dickenson, Lee, Russell, Scott, Washington, Wise, and the cities of Bristol and Norton. </p>
</div>



</div></div><div class="sqs-block button-block sqs-block-button" data-block-type="53" id="block-yui_3_17_2_1_1557135938881_6430"><div class="sqs-block-content">

