<div class="sqs-html-content">
  <h3 style="white-space:pre-wrap;"><strong>TODD IS A PROVEN LEADER, GETTING RESULTS ON ISSUES THAT MATTER MOST TO SOUTHWEST VIRGINIANS.</strong></h3><ul data-rte-list="default"><li><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;">JOBS AND THE ECONOMY</p></li><li><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;">STANDING UP FOR SWVA VALUES</p></li><li><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;">FIGHTING BACK AGAINST OPIOID ADDICTION</p></li></ul>
