    <div class="index-section-wrapper page-content">
      <div class="content-inner has-content" data-content-field="main-content">
        <div class="sqs-layout sqs-grid-12 columns-12" data-type="page" data-updated-on="1679060729127" id="page-5ccc120f971a1850c2c729b1"><div class="row sqs-row"><div class="col sqs-col-6 span-6"><div class="sqs-block html-block sqs-block-html" data-block-type="2" id="block-715473a1969ae6976a34"><div class="sqs-block-content">

<div class="sqs-html-content">
  <p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;">My office is available to assist you in matters involving the government of the Commonwealth of Virginia.&nbsp;Additionally, for matters under the purview of federal or local government, we can refer your request to the appropriate entity. If you need assistance with any state agency, please do not hesitate to contact my office.</p><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;">Examples of state agencies we assist with:</p><ul data-rte-list="default"><li><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;">Department of Motor Vehicles</p></li><li><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;">Department of Transportation</p></li><li><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;">Department of Medical Assistance Services</p></li><li><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;">Department of Social Services</p></li><li><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;">Department of Taxation </p></li></ul>
</div>



